provides a theoretical justification to the\nuse of weak automata as symbolic representations of sets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jan 2010 17:40:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Feb 2010 16:34:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-01"}
