s are\nconnected. A part of our results is relevant to the color superconductivity of\nquarks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jan 2010 20:43:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2010 22:13:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 5 Apr 2010 19:50:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-04-14"}
