ion of the observations of distant galaxies is\nparticularly strengthened in this case.\n  This object is amongst the best example on how one may misinterpret\nmorphology in the absence of kinematical information.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jan 2010 21:19:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Jan 2010 21:08:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
